title: Pound Audio - Sensation Orchestra
description:
'Sensation Orchestra' is finally here knocking at your door. This awesome product brings you 12 Orchestral String elements in the styles of Hip Hop, Dirty South, West Coast, Jazz, and many more. Pound Audio has made sure to create several different styles within one product.

This awesome pack contains carefully crafted rich string elements with a Hip Hop, Dirty South, East Coast, West Coast, and Jazz Orchestral Genre that will allow you to add a wide range of Orchestral tones to your productions.
